{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-075","title":"Sentence 75","sectionId":"sentences-071","sectionTitle":"Sentence 71-80","pageStart":489,"pageEnd":495,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":25,"duplicateEntryCount":15,"pages":[{"number":489,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 75"},{"type":"text","text":"The residence time is the average length of time that any particular"},{"type":"text","text":"molecule of water remains in the lake, and it is calculated by dividing the"},{"type":"text","text":"volume of water in the lake by the rate at which water leaves the lake."},{"type":"text","text":"停留时间指的是特定水分子在湖中停留的平均时长。这是通过"},{"type":"text","text":"将湖水量除以水流出湖泊的速度计算出来的。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"这是一个由and连接的并列复合句。第一个分句的主干是The"},{"type":"text","text":"residence time is the average length of time，其后由that引导一个定语从"},{"type":"text","text":"句。第二个分句的主干是“It is calculated by ...”，其中定语从句at which"},{"type":"text","text":"water leaves the lake修饰前面的名词the rate。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"residence /ˈrezɪdəns/ n. 住房；居住","headword":"residence"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 re（重新）+sid（坐）+ence→重新坐下→安定下来→居住"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 residence time停留时间，逗留时间"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 dwelling n. 住处"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 reside vi. 定居；在于"},{"type":"text","text":"residency n. 住处"},{"type":"entry","text":"particular /pərˈtɪkjələr/ a. 特定的；独特的；详细的；挑剔的 n. 详","headword":"particular"},{"type":"text","text":"情，细目"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 part（部分）+icular（属于…的）→只属于部分的→特定的"}]},{"number":490,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"同根 particularly ad. 特别，尤其"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 peculiar a. 奇特的"},{"type":"entry","text":"molecule /ˈmɑːlɪkjuːl/ n. 分子","headword":"molecule"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 mole（=mol堆）+cule（小的）→很小的东西堆在一起→分"},{"type":"text","text":"子"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 molecular a. 分子的；分子组成的"},{"type":"entry","text":"volume /ˈvɑːljuːm/ n. 量；体积；音量；卷","headword":"volume"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 vol（卷）+ume→装订成卷→卷，册"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 amount n. 量"},{"type":"text","text":"capacity n. 容积"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"}]},{"number":491,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"与“江，河，湖，海”相关的词："},{"type":"text","text":"barrier lake堰塞湖"},{"type":"entry","text":"brook /brʊk/ n. 小溪","headword":"brook"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 stream n. 溪流"},{"type":"text","text":"rivulet n. 小溪，小河"},{"type":"entry","text":"coastal /ˈkoʊstl/ a. 沿海的；沿岸的","headword":"coastal"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 coastal city 沿海城市"},{"type":"entry","text":"corrugate /ˈkɒrʊˌɡeɪt/ v. （使）起波浪；起皱纹","headword":"corrugate"}]},{"number":492,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"/ˈkɒrʊɡɪt/ a. 起皱的；波状的"},{"type":"entry","text":"crack /kræk/ n. 龟裂 v. 破裂","headword":"crack"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 cracked a. 有裂纹的"},{"type":"text","text":"cracking n. 裂纹"},{"type":"entry","text":"downstream /ˌdaʊnˈstriːm/ a./ad. 在下游","headword":"downstream"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 down（下）+stream（溪流）→在下游"},{"type":"entry","text":"embankment /ɪmˈbæŋkmənt/ n. 堤","headword":"embankment"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 embank vt. 筑堤"},{"type":"entry","text":"fountain /ˈfaʊntn/ n. 喷泉","headword":"fountain"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 山（mountain）里有喷泉（fountain）"},{"type":"entry","text":"gulley /ˈɡʌli/ n. 溪沟","headword":"gulley"},{"type":"entry","text":"hydrology /haɪˈdrɑːlədʒi/ n. 水文地理学","headword":"hydrology"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 hydrological a. 水文学的"},{"type":"entry","text":"inlet /ˈɪnlet/ n. 水湾；入口","headword":"inlet"},{"type":"note","text":"反义 outlet n. 出口"},{"type":"entry","text":"island /ˈaɪlənd/ n. 岛屿","headword":"island"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 isolated island 孤岛"}]},{"number":493,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"maritime /ˈmærɪtaɪm/ a. 海的；航海的；沿海的","headword":"maritime"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 mari（海）+time（时间）→海上的时间→航海的"},{"type":"entry","text":"midstream /ˌmɪdˈstriːm/ n. 中游","headword":"midstream"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 mid（中）+stream（溪流）→中游"},{"type":"text","text":"mineral spring 矿泉"},{"type"